verse.lines:
"This is She,
the Bride of the last days,
Who stood the worst of times,
when so many slipped away;
Here's your crown,
take your place beside the Throne,
I am now your very own;
This is the special Chosen One you see;
this is She!"

You are She,
the Bride of the last days,
Who stood the worst of times,
when so many slipped away;
Here's your crown,
take your place beside the Throne,
Christ is now your very own;
This is the special Chosen One you see;
You are She! You are She!
